    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner today! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this car handles beautifully and feels great behind the wheel. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a great home. Come by and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example features the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox, providing a tactile connection to the limited-slip rear differential. Technical highlights include a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate chassis fatigue and a recently refreshed cooling system with a high-flow water pump. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the precise turn-in and hydraulic steering feedback these longitudinal-engine platforms are known for. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain maintains exceptional thermal efficiency and compression, making it a driver-centric example ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Interior clean. Minor exterior wear. Maintenance records available. Title in hand.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you\u2019ll find the expected minor road peppering on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium leather seats remain supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the crisp infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has been fastidiously maintained with a documented service history, ensuring the engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision. Recent tire replacement and a fresh fluid service mean it\u2019s ready for the road immediately. This is an honest, dependable car that looks as good as it drives.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
