      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and long-term reliability. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. A premier choice for the discerning driver seeking refined quality and proven value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
