      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it for its next owner! It\u2019s super reliable, handles the road like a champ, and has been a total rockstar for my daily commutes. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. If you're looking for a dependable car that's ready for its next adventure, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
