      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This FD3S RX-7 features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, delivering linear power through a crisp 5-speed manual transmission. The chassis maintains its celebrated 50/50 weight distribution with a rigid double-wishbone suspension setup. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and a vacuum line simplification to ensure boost stability across the primary and secondary turbines. The Torsen limited-slip differential remains tight, providing exceptional corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the mechanical fundamentals\u2014including strong compression pulses across both rotors\u2014make this a high-performance, driver-focused example ready for the circuit.",
